name: sphinxcontrib-redoc
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "sphinxcontrib-redoc" %}
{% set version = "1.6.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: e358edbe23927d36432dde748e978cf897283a331a03e93d3ef02e348dee4561

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 1
  script: '{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vv '

requirements:
  host:
    - setuptools_scm
    - pip
    - python

  run:
    - jinja2 >=2.4
    - python
    - six >=1.5
    - sphinx >=1.5
    - jsonschema >=3.0
    - PyYAML >=3.12

test:
  imports:
    - sphinxcontrib.redoc

about:
  home: https://github.com/ikalnytskyi/sphinxcontrib-redoc
  license: BSD-2-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: ReDoc powered OpenAPI (fka Swagger) spec renderer for Sphinx
  doc_url: https://sphinxcontrib-redoc.readthedocs.io
  dev_url: https://github.com/ikalnytskyi/sphinxcontrib-redoc

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - mxr-conda
    - agcopenhaver
    - oblute
    - rluria14
smithy_version:
No azure token. Create a token and
put it in ~/.conda-smithy/azure.token
